{"type":"message","id":"bc90a9da","parentId":"2c415e49","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:39:49.711Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-01 09:39:49 GMT+8] Feishu[main] DM from ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209: 专用密码 FNRZRg8gHF9KqeSn 该密码可用作在第三方邮箱客户端登录飞书邮箱，为了账号安全，请勿泄露给他人 相关配置参数 邮箱地址 liuwei@gaowei.com 收信服务器（IMAP） imap.feishu.cn 使用 SSL，端口号：993 发信服务器（SMTP） smtp.feishu.cn 使用\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b550dc08acca8b285b22b182e237\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209\"\n}\n```\n\n专用密码\nFNRZRg8gHF9KqeSn\n该密码可用作在第三方邮箱客户端登录飞书邮箱，为了账号安全，请勿泄露给他人\n\n相关配置参数\n邮箱地址\nliuwei@gaowei.com\n收信服务器（IMAP）\nimap.feishu.cn\n使用 SSL，端口号：993\n发信服务器（SMTP）\nsmtp.feishu.cn\n使用 SSL，端口号：465"}],"timestamp":1772329189710}}
{"type":"message","id":"926c0d62","parentId":"bc90a9da","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:40:01.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"伟哥给了我飞书邮箱的SMTP配置信息。这是敏感信息，我需要：\n1. 把这些信息安全地保存起来（但不要明文保存密码到公开文件）\n2. 尝试用这些配置发邮件给碧容\n\n让我先试试能不能通过命令行发邮件。我可以用Python或者其他工具来发送SMTP邮件。\n\n配置信息：\n- 邮箱地址: liuwei@gaowei.com\n- SMTP服务器: smtp.feishu.cn\n- 端口: 465 (SSL)\n- 密码: FNRZRg8gHF9KqeSn\n\n收件人：碧容 cbr@gaowei.com\n\n我应该先更新TOOLS.md记录邮箱配置（但不要明文记录密码），然后尝试发送邮件。\n\n实际上，为了安全性，我应该把密码存到一个安全的地方，或者用环境变量。但现在先试试发邮件功能是否可用。\n\n让我用Python写一个简单的脚本来发送邮件。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"收到配置！我先试试发邮件给碧容。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_018btBrF1xMgQSJgP1X5Syjt","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\nfrom email.mime.multipart import MIMEMultipart\n\n# 配置\nsmtp_server = \"smtp.feishu.cn\"\nsmtp_port = 465\nsender_email = \"liuwei@gaowei.com\"\nsender_password = \"FNRZRg8gHF9KqeSn\"\nrecipient_email = \"cbr@gaowei.com\"\n\n# 邮件内容\nmsg = MIMEMultipart()\nmsg['From'] = sender_email\nmsg['To'] = recipient_email\nmsg['Subject'] = \"早上好 ☀️\"\n\nbody = \"\"\"碧容，\n\n早上好！\n\n祝你今天工作顺利！\n\n伟哥\n\"\"\"\n\nmsg.attach(MIMEText(body, 'plain', 'utf-8'))\n\ntry:\n    server = smtplib.SMTP_SSL(smtp_server, smtp_port)\n    server.login(sender_email, sender_password)\n    server.sendmail(sender_email, recipient_email, msg.as_string())\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"✅ 邮件发送成功！\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"❌ 发送失败: {e}\")\nEOF"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":741,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":20799,"totalTokens":21550,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772329189712}}
