{"type":"message","id":"e77d42ff","parentId":"f20799fd","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:51:28.372Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-01 09:51:28 GMT+8] Feishu[main] DM from ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209: 飞书日程创建 — 3月2日（周一）教学中心集中办公 - 时间：10:00-16:00 - 地点：教学中心 - 参与人：你、雯祯、大眼\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b550df737a0a4b273e355989ed96\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209\"\n}\n```\n\n飞书日程创建 — 3月2日（周一）教学中心集中办公\n  - 时间：10:00-16:00\n  - 地点：教学中心\n  - 参与人：你、雯祯、大眼"}],"timestamp":1772329888370}}
{"type":"message","id":"538573a4","parentId":"e77d42ff","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:51:35.103Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"伟哥要我创建一个飞书日程。我需要使用 feishu_calendar 工具来创建日程。\n\n参数：\n- 日期：3月2日（周一），也就是 2026-03-02\n- 时间：10:00-16:00\n- 地点：教学中心\n- 参与人：伟哥自己、雯祯、大眼\n\n我需要先查找这些人的 open_id。让我用 feishu_contact 来搜索。\n\n先读一下 feishu-calendar 的 skill 文件看看怎么用。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01Dt3795T8SHCWvC6ndHNUMj","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-calendar/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01JqNY9JzHukQpdfF8CkLpXo","name":"feishu_contact","arguments":{"action":"search","query":"雯祯"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_011sp3WEgouWFX9rUmzxM7FS","name":"feishu_contact","arguments":{"action":"search","query":"大眼"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":362,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":24249,"totalTokens":24621,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772329888372}}
{"type":"message","id":"34d48598","parentId":"538573a4","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:51:35.115Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01Dt3795T8SHCWvC6ndHNUMj","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-calendar\ndescription: |\n  Feishu calendar event management. Create, update, delete, and retrieve calendar events. Requires calendar:calendar.event:create and related permissions.\n---\n\n# Feishu Calendar Tool\n\nManage Feishu calendar events using the `feishu_calendar` tool.\n\n## Actions\n\n### Create Event\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create\",\n  \"summary\": \"教学中心集中办公\",\n  \"description\": \"教学中心集中办公讨论\",\n  \"start_time\": \"2025-03-02T10:00:00+08:00\",\n  \"end_time\": \"2025-03-02T16:00:00+08:00\",\n  \"location\": \"教学中心\",\n  \"attendees\": [\"ou_xxx\", \"ou_yyy\"]\n}\n```\n\n### Get Event\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"get\",\n  \"event_id\": \"event_xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n### Update Event\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"update\",\n  \"event_id\": \"event_xxx\",\n  \"summary\": \"Updated Title\",\n  \"start_time\": \"2025-03-02T11:00:00+08:00\"\n}\n```\n\n### Delete Event\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"delete\",\n  \"event_id\": \"event_xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n- `action` - Required: create, update, delete, get\n- `summary` - Event title\n- `description` - Event description\n- `start_time` - ISO 8601 timestamp (e.g., 2025-03-02T10:00:00+08:00)\n- `end_time` - ISO 8601 timestamp\n- `location` - Location name\n- `attendees` - Array of user open_ids\n- `visibility` - default, public, or private\n\n## Permissions Required\n\n- `calendar:calendar.event:create` - Create events\n- `calendar:calendar.event:update` - Update events\n- `calendar:calendar.event:delete` - Delete events\n- `calendar:calendar.event:read` - Read events\n\n## Usage Notes\n\n- Times should be in ISO 8601 format with timezone\n- Attendees should be user open_ids (not emails or names)\n- Use feishu_contact tool to find user open_ids\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772329895111}}
