{"type":"message","id":"5c137ed5","parentId":"ce11c85e","timestamp":"2026-03-01T01:58:05.136Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是搜不到。部门列表API一直报400。这可能是API权限问题，而不是通讯录范围问题。让我检查一下我们有哪些通讯录相关的权限...\n\n从之前feishu_app_scopes的结果看，我们有：\n- contact:user.base:readonly\n- contact:contact.base:readonly\n- contact:department.base:readonly\n- contact:user:search (user类型)\n\n可能需要申请 contact:department:readonly 或类似的权限来列出部门。\n\n或者问题出在API实现上。不管怎样，现在最快的解决办法是让伟哥直接给我邮箱。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"还是不行，部门API一直报400 🤔\n\n看起来是API权限问题，不单是范围问题。可能需要在「权限管理」里申请这个权限：\n- `contact:department.organize:readonly` - 获取部门组织架构\n\n不过现在先别折腾了——**直接给我他俩邮箱**，我先把日程建了，权限问题咱们后面再慢慢调。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":325,"cacheRead":37067,"cacheWrite":412,"totalTokens":37812,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772330277283}}
