{"type":"message","id":"0a007c3b","parentId":"eb4765f6","timestamp":"2026-03-01T02:00:02.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"伟哥在搜索 contact:department 权限。我看到有三个相关权限：\n\n1. `contact:department.base:readonly` - 获取部门基础信息\n2. `contact:department.hrbp:readonly` - 查询部门HRBP信息\n3. `contact:department.organize:readonly` - 获取通讯录部门组织架构信息\n\n第三个 `contact:department.organize:readonly` 是我刚才提到的那个。我之前查权限时显示已经有这个权限了，但API还是报400...\n\n让我想想，可能需要勾选这三个权限都申请一下，然后重新发布版本。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"对！就是这三个，全勾上：\n\n- ☑️ `contact:department.base:readonly` - 获取部门基础信息\n- ☑️ `contact:department.hrbp:readonly` - 查询部门HRBP信息  \n- ☑️ `contact:department.organize:readonly` - 获取通讯录部门组织架构信息\n\n勾完点「确认开通权限」，然后**重新创建版本发布**。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":327,"cacheRead":37479,"cacheWrite":2207,"totalTokens":40023,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772330393534}}
