{"type":"message","id":"d22f83ca","parentId":"fd6dc79f","timestamp":"2026-03-01T02:01:13.767Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"伟哥在问我的身份，可能是在问我用什么身份调用飞书API——是用 tenant_access_token（应用身份）还是 user_access_token（用户身份）？\n\n这是一个很好的问题。飞书API有两种调用身份：\n1. 应用身份（tenant_access_token）- 以应用的名义调用\n2. 用户身份（user_access_token）- 以用户的名义调用\n\n从之前的权限列表看，有些权限只有 user 类型，比如 `contact:user:search`。如果我用的是 tenant_access_token，可能就调不了需要 user_access_token 的API。\n\n我需要查一下 OpenClaw 是用什么身份调用飞书API的。让我检查一下...","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！这可能是关键。\n\n飞书API有两种调用身份：\n- **应用身份** (tenant_access_token) — 以应用名义调用\n- **用户身份** (user_access_token) — 以你的名义调用\n\n从之前看权限列表，`contact:user:search` 这个搜索权限是 **user 类型**，意味着可能需要用用户身份才能调用。\n\n让我查一下我实际用的是哪个身份..."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01QzYcGVZ2FKcFHERLH2R9zk","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -r \"access_token\" ~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/ --include=\"*.ts\" --include=\"*.js\" | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":463,"cacheRead":41480,"cacheWrite":710,"totalTokens":42663,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772330465320}}
