{"type":"message","id":"3dbdbc2a","parentId":"f651bf9c","timestamp":"2026-03-01T02:22:00.519Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-01 10:22:00 GMT+8] Feishu[main] DM from ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209: 改成：claude-opus-4-5 试试\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b550d79f53ca0b38efd276bca66e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_b89c76c98db6919ae2dacdc44d876209\"\n}\n```\n\n改成：claude-opus-4-5   试试"}],"timestamp":1772331720517}}
{"type":"message","id":"fdd9b34f","parentId":"3dbdbc2a","timestamp":"2026-03-01T02:22:09.950Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这看起来是一条重复的旧消息（之前出现过相同的内容和 message_id）。伟哥之前已经尝试改模型名了，现在应该已经在正常对话中了。我应该忽略这条重复消息，或者简单确认一下我们现在在哪里。\n\n实际上这可能是系统重发的消息。让我继续之前的对话 - 我们在debug飞书通讯录权限的问题。我建议他去「测试企业和人员」或者飞书管理后台看看。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"这条是之前的消息重发了～ 我们刚才在查飞书通讯录权限。\n\n你去「测试企业和人员」或者飞书管理后台看了吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":232,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":49196,"totalTokens":49438,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772331720519}}
