{"type":"message","id":"98338aa7","parentId":"5bea3deb","timestamp":"2026-03-01T05:23:16.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"伟哥说根目录下没有人，只有部门，人在部门下面。这说明问题是我们只能看到根部门(id=0)，但看不到子部门。需要修改代码来：\n1. 递归获取子部门\n2. 或者传入 `fetch_child: true` 参数来获取子部门\n\n让我看看飞书API文档关于 department.list 的参数...实际上，根据飞书API，`department.list` 默认只返回直接子部门。需要设置 `parent_department_id` 来获取特定部门的子部门，或者递归调用。\n\n让我修改代码，让它能获取子部门。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！代码只获取了根部门，没有递归获取子部门。我来修："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_014jbDRUf9S7iVi7gGhNh4y7","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/src/contact.ts","limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":318,"cacheRead":53641,"cacheWrite":720,"totalTokens":54689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772342588822}}
{"type":"message","id":"6758ae74","parentId":"98338aa7","timestamp":"2026-03-01T05:23:16.361Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_014jbDRUf9S7iVi7gGhNh4y7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import type * as Lark from \"@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk\";\nimport type { OpenClawPluginApi } from \"openclaw/plugin-sdk\";\nimport { listEnabledFeishuAccounts } from \"./accounts.js\";\nimport { createFeishuClient } from \"./client.js\";\nimport { FeishuContactSchema, type FeishuContactParams } from \"./contact-schema.js\";\nimport { resolveToolsConfig } from \"./tools-config.js\";\n\nfunction json(data: unknown) {\n  return {\n    content: [{ type: \"text\" as const, text: JSON.stringify(data, null, 2) }],\n    details: data,\n  };\n}\n\nasync function searchUsers(client: Lark.Client, query: string): Promise<{ users: any[]; debug?: any }> {\n  const users: any[] = [];\n  const debug: any = { steps: [], departments: [] };\n  const lowerQuery = query.toLowerCase();\n\n  // First, list all departments to see what's available\n  try {\n    debug.steps.push(\"Listing departments...\");\n    const deptResp: any = await client.contact.department.list({ params: { page_size: 50 } });\n    if (deptResp.code === 0 && deptResp.data?.items) {\n      debug.departments = deptResp.data.items.map((d: any) => ({ id: d.department_id, name: d.name }));\n      debug.steps.push(`Found ${debug.departments.length} departments`);\n    }\n  } catch (e: any) {\n    debug.steps.push(`Department list error: ${e.message || e}`);\n  }\n\n  // Try list API for each department\n  for (const dept of debug.departments.slice(0, 5)) {\n    try {\n      debug.steps.push(`Trying department ${dept.name} (${dept.id})...`);\n      const resp: any = await client.contact.user.findByDepartment({\n        params: { department_id: dept.id, page_size: 50 }\n      });\n      \n      if (resp.code === 0 && resp.data?.items) {\n        debug.steps.push(`Dept ${dept.name}: ${resp.data.items.length} users`);\n        \n        for (const u of resp.data.items) {\n          const name = (u.name || \"\").toLowerCase();\n          if (name.includes(lowerQuery)) {\n            users.push({ open_id: u.open_id, name: u.name, email: u.email, employee_id: u.employee_id, mobile: u.mobile });\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      debug.steps.push(`Dept ${dept.name} error: ${e.message || e}`);\n    }\n    \n    if (users.length > 0) break;\n  }\n\n  // Try list API\n  try {\n    debug.steps.push(\"Trying list API...\");\n    let pageToken: string | undefined;\n    let pageCount = 0;\n    \n    do {\n      pageCount++;\n      const resp: any = await client.contact.user.list({ \n        params: { page_size: 50, page_token: pageToken } \n      });\n      \n      if (resp.code !== 0) {\n        debug.steps.push(`List API error: ${resp.msg || resp.code}`);\n        break;\n      }\n      \n      const items = resp.data?.items || [];\n      debug.steps.push(`Page ${pageCount}: ${items.length} users`);\n      \n      for (const u of items) {\n        const name = (u.name || \"\").toLowerCase();\n        const email = (u.email || \"\").toLowerCase();\n        const empId = (u.employee_id || \"\").toLowerCase();\n\n[69 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772342596358}}
{"type":"message","id":"83af13e2","parentId":"6758ae74","timestamp":"2026-03-01T05:23:22.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了。代码调用 `department.list()` 时没有传 `parent_department_id`，所以只返回根部门的直接子部门。但如果应用的通讯录可见范围设置不包括根部门，就只能看到一个空的根部门。让我修改代码来：\n1. 先获取根部门下的子部门（传入 `parent_department_id: \"0\"`）\n2. 然后递归获取每个子部门下的用户\n\n或者更简单的方式是，设置 `fetch_child: true` 参数来获取所有子部门。\n\n让我查看一下飞书API文档...实际上，`department.list` 有一个 `fetch_child` 参数，设置为 true 可以获取所有子部门。\n\n让我修改代码。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01LCm9VBQqd4vR9j7M16LmDn","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/src/contact.ts","old_string":"const deptResp: any = await client.contact.department.list({ params: { page_size: 50 } });","new_string":"const deptResp: any = await client.contact.department.list({ params: { page_size: 50, fetch_child: true, parent_department_id: \"0\" } });"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":418,"cacheRead":54361,"cacheWrite":1300,"totalTokens":56087,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772342596361}}
{"type":"message","id":"0b90a5b2","parentId":"83af13e2","timestamp":"2026-03-01T05:23:22.718Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01LCm9VBQqd4vR9j7M16LmDn","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in ~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/src/contact.ts."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  19 \n  20   // First, list all departments to see what's available\n  21   try {\n  22     debug.steps.push(\"Listing departments...\");\n- 23     const deptResp: any = await client.contact.department.list({ params: { page_size: 50 } });\n+ 23     const deptResp: any = await client.contact.department.list({ params: { page_size: 50, fetch_child: true, parent_department_id: \"0\" } });\n  24     if (deptResp.code === 0 && deptResp.data?.items) {\n  25       debug.departments = deptResp.data.items.map((d: any) => ({ id: d.department_id, name: d.name }));\n  26       debug.steps.push(`Found ${debug.departments.length} departments`);\n  27     }\n     ...","firstChangedLine":23},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772342602713}}
