{"type":"message","id":"7ccd568a","parentId":"1b406249","timestamp":"2026-03-01T05:26:47.824Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"有大进展了！现在能查到22个部门了！但是获取部门下用户时报400错误。让我去飞书日志看看这个400是什么错误...不过我可以先猜测一下，可能是 `findByDepartment` API的参数有问题，或者page_size也超限了。让我检查一下代码中 `findByDepartment` 的调用。\n\n从代码看：\n```typescript\nconst resp: any = await client.contact.user.findByDepartment({\n  params: { department_id: dept.id, page_size: 50 }\n});\n```\n\n这个API的参数格式可能不对。让我查一下飞书SDK的正确用法...实际上，`findByDepartment` 可能需要用 `path` 来传 department_id，而不是 `params`。\n\n或者更可能的是，这个API在飞书SDK里的方法名不对。让我用 `user.list` 加上 `department_id` 参数来替代。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"有进展！**查到22个部门了！** 🎉\n\n但是查部门下的用户报400。让我修一下获取用户的API调用："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01QsYeNkuN2RkH8ALJG6AyXd","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/src/contact.ts","old_string":"const resp: any = await client.contact.user.findByDepartment({\n        params: { department_id: dept.id, page_size: 50 }\n      });","new_string":"const resp: any = await client.contact.user.list({\n        params: { department_id: dept.id, page_size: 50 }\n      });"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":520,"cacheRead":56654,"cacheWrite":1298,"totalTokens":58480,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772342798664}}
