{"type":"message","id":"81fe3177","parentId":"8487d637","timestamp":"2026-03-01T05:42:42.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还是0用户。从debug看，查询部门下用户没有输出任何结果（没有报错也没有返回用户数）。可能是代码里查询部门用户的部分根本没执行，或者执行了但没有输出日志。\n\n让我检查代码逻辑——当找到部门后，应该会尝试查询每个部门下的用户并输出 \"Dept xxx: N users\"，但现在只看到 \"Trying department xxx...\"，没有后续输出。\n\n这说明查询部门用户的API调用可能失败了但没有被记录。让我看看代码：\n\n```typescript\nfor (const dept of debug.departments.slice(0, 5)) {\n    try {\n      debug.steps.push(`Trying department ${dept.name} (${dept.id})...`);\n      const resp: any = await client.contact.user.list({\n        params: { department_id: dept.id, page_size: 50 }\n      });\n      \n      if (resp.code === 0 && resp.data?.items) {\n        debug.steps.push(`Dept ${dept.name}: ${resp.data.items.length} users`);\n        ...\n      }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      debug.steps.push(`Dept ${dept.name} error: ${e.message || e}`);\n    }\n```\n\n没有输出 \"Dept xxx: N users\" 或 error，说明：\n1. `resp.code !== 0` 但没有抛异常\n2. 或者 `resp.data?.items` 是undefined\n\n让我修改代码，增加更多日志输出。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"没有输出部门下的用户数，可能API返回了非0的code但没被记录。让我加更多日志："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01SmCJ6Yk9GGj9i4mUKDkge6","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/src/contact.ts","offset":30,"limit":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":581,"cacheRead":64066,"cacheWrite":1751,"totalTokens":66406,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772343752042}}
{"type":"message","id":"b6e7b417","parentId":"81fe3177","timestamp":"2026-03-01T05:42:42.646Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01SmCJ6Yk9GGj9i4mUKDkge6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"  }\n\n  // Try list API for each department\n  for (const dept of debug.departments.slice(0, 5)) {\n    try {\n      debug.steps.push(`Trying department ${dept.name} (${dept.id})...`);\n      const resp: any = await client.contact.user.list({\n        params: { open_department_id: dept.id, page_size: 50 }\n      });\n      \n      if (resp.code === 0 && resp.data?.items) {\n        debug.steps.push(`Dept ${dept.name}: ${resp.data.items.length} users`);\n        \n        for (const u of resp.data.items) {\n          const name = (u.name || \"\").toLowerCase();\n          if (name.includes(lowerQuery)) {\n            users.push({ open_id: u.open_id, name: u.name, email: u.email, employee_id: u.employee_id, mobile: u.mobile });\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    } catch (e: any) {\n      debug.steps.push(`Dept ${dept.name} error: ${e.message || e}`);\n    }\n    \n    if (users.length > 0) break;\n  }\n\n  // Try list API\n  try {\n    debug.steps.push(\"Trying list API...\");\n\n[90 more lines in file. Use offset=60 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772343762641}}
