{"type":"message","id":"18b931f6","parentId":"6d047cad","timestamp":"2026-03-01T05:45:32.102Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到问题了！`code=0, msg=success, items=undefined`\n\nAPI返回成功(code=0)，但是 `items` 是 undefined。这说明返回的数据结构不对，可能是：1. 用户数据不在 `resp.data.items` 里，而在其他字段\n2. 或者需要不同的参数\n\n让我检查一下飞书API文档。根据飞书文档，获取部门直属用户列表的API是 `/open-apis/contact/v3/users/find_by_department`，不是 `/open-apis/contact/v3/users`。\n\n`/open-apis/contact/v3/users` 是获取全量用户列表，需要传 `department_id` 参数来过滤，返回的数据结构是 `data.items`。\n\n但我用的是 `client.contact.user.list`，可能SDK的返回格式不一样。让我输出完整的 resp 看看。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！`code=0, msg=success, items=undefined`\n\nAPI成功返回，但 `items` 是 undefined。数据可能在其他字段。让我加更多日志看看返回结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01FvMvV7123w3jJEKRqLZtM7","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/src/contact.ts","old_string":"debug.steps.push(`Dept ${dept.name} resp: code=${resp.code}, msg=${resp.msg}, items=${resp.data?.items?.length}`);","new_string":"debug.steps.push(`Dept ${dept.name} resp: code=${resp.code}, msg=${resp.msg}, data_keys=${Object.keys(resp.data || {}).join(',')}, items=${resp.data?.items?.length}`);"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":8,"output":532,"cacheRead":67846,"cacheWrite":1634,"totalTokens":70020,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772343923278}}
