{"type":"message","id":"8b7fe99a","parentId":"3449b23c","timestamp":"2026-03-01T06:34:54.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说没有新的报错日志，这意味着飞书API可能没有收到请求，或者请求成功了但没有返回数据。让我检查一下 feishu_calendar 工具的代码，看看它是如何实现的。\n\n之前返回空对象 `{}`，可能是工具没有正确返回结果。让我看看 feishu_calendar 的代码实现。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"那可能是API请求没发出去，或者工具没返回结果。让我检查日历工具的代码："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:98","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/src/calendar.ts"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":62432,"output":109,"cacheRead":10496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73037,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772346874740}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a876b7f","parentId":"8b7fe99a","timestamp":"2026-03-01T06:34:54.635Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read:98","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import type * as Lark from \"@larksuiteoapi/node-sdk\";\nimport type { OpenClawPluginApi } from \"openclaw/plugin-sdk\";\nimport { listEnabledFeishuAccounts } from \"./accounts.js\";\nimport { createFeishuClient } from \"./client.js\";\nimport { FeishuCalendarSchema } from \"./calendar-schema.js\";\nimport type { FeishuCalendarParams } from \"./calendar-schema.js\";\nimport { resolveToolsConfig } from \"./tools-config.js\";\n\nfunction json(data: unknown) {\n  return {\n    content: [{ type: \"text\" as const, text: JSON.stringify(data, null, 2) }],\n    details: data,\n  };\n}\n\n// Convert ISO time to Feishu timestamp (seconds)\nfunction toTimestamp(isoTime: string): number {\n  return Math.floor(new Date(isoTime).getTime() / 1000);\n}\n\nasync function createEvent(client: Lark.Client, params: FeishuCalendarParams) {\n  if (!params.summary || !params.start_time || !params.end_time) {\n    return { error: \"Missing required fields: summary, start_time, end_time\" };\n  }\n\n  const body: any = {\n    summary: params.summary,\n    description: params.description || \"\",\n    start_time: { timestamp: toTimestamp(params.start_time), timezone: \"Asia/Shanghai\" },\n    end_time: { timestamp: toTimestamp(params.end_time), timezone: \"Asia/Shanghai\" },\n    visibility: params.visibility || \"default\",\n  };\n\n  if (params.location) {\n    body.location = { name: params.location };\n  }\n\n  if (params.attendees && params.attendees.length > 0) {\n    body.attendees = params.attendees.map((id) => ({\n      type: \"user\",\n      user_id: id,\n    }));\n  }\n\n  const resp: any = await client.calendar.calendar.create({\n    path: { calendar_id: \"primary\" },\n    data: body,\n  });\n\n  if (resp.code !== 0) {\n    throw new Error(resp.msg || `Failed to create event: ${resp.code}`);\n  }\n\n  return {\n    event_id: resp.data?.event?.event_id,\n    summary: resp.data?.event?.summary,\n    start_time: resp.data?.event?.start_time,\n    end_time: resp.data?.event?.end_time,\n    attendees: resp.data?.event?.attendees,\n  };\n}\n\nasync function getEvent(client: Lark.Client, eventId: string) {\n  const resp: any = await client.calendar.calendarEvent.get({\n    path: { calendar_id: \"primary\", event_id: eventId },\n  });\n\n  if (resp.code !== 0) {\n    throw new Error(resp.msg || `Failed to get event: ${resp.code}`);\n  }\n\n  return resp.data?.event;\n}\n\nasync function updateEvent(client: Lark.Client, eventId: string, params: FeishuCalendarParams) {\n  const body: any = {};\n  \n  if (params.summary) body.summary = params.summary;\n  if (params.description !== undefined) body.description = params.description;\n  if (params.start_time) {\n    body.start_time = { timestamp: toTimestamp(params.start_time), timezone: \"Asia/Shanghai\" };\n  }\n  if (params.end_time) {\n    body.end_time = { timestamp: toTimestamp(params.end_time), timezone: \"Asia/Shanghai\" };\n  }\n  if (params.location) body.location = { name: params.location };\n  if (params.visibility) body.visibility = params.visibility;\n  \n  if (params.attendees) {\n    body.attendees = params.attendees.map((id) => ({\n      type: \"user\",\n      user_id: id,\n    }));\n  }\n\n  const resp: any = await client.calendar.calendarEvent.patch({\n    path: { calendar_id: \"primary\", event_id: eventId },\n    data: body,\n  });\n\n  if (resp.code !== 0) {\n    throw new Error(resp.msg || `Failed to update event: ${resp.code}`);\n  }\n\n  return { event_id: eventId, updated: true };\n}\n\nasync function deleteEvent(client: Lark.Client, eventId: string) {\n  const resp: any = await client.calendar.calendarEvent.delete({\n    path: { calendar_id: \"primary\", event_id: eventId },\n  });\n\n  if (resp.code !== 0) {\n    throw new Error(resp.msg || `Failed to delete event: ${resp.code}`);\n  }\n\n  return { event_id: eventId, deleted: true };\n}\n\nexport function registerFeishuCalendarTools(api: OpenClawPluginApi) {\n  const accounts = listEnabledFeishuAccounts(api.config);\n  if (accounts.length === 0) return;\n\n  const firstAccount = accounts[0];\n  const toolsCfg = resolveToolsConfig(firstAccount.config.tools);\n  if (toolsCfg.calendar === false) return;\n\n  const getClient = () => createFeishuClient(firstAccount);\n\n  api.registerTool({\n    name: \"feishu_calendar\",\n    label: \"Feishu Calendar\",\n    description: \"Create and manage Feishu calendar events. Actions: create, update, delete, get\",\n    parameters: FeishuCalendarSchema,\n    async execute(_toolCallId, params) {\n      const p = params as FeishuCalendarParams;\n      try {\n        const client = getClient();\n        \n        if (p.action === \"create\") {\n          return json(await createEvent(client, p));\n        }\n        \n        if (p.action === \"get\") {\n          if (!p.event_id) return json({ error: \"Missing event_id\" });\n          return json(await getEvent(client, p.event_id));\n        }\n        \n        if (p.action === \"update\") {\n          if (!p.event_id) return json({ error: \"Missing event_id\" });\n          return json(await updateEvent(client, p.event_id, p));\n        }\n        \n        if (p.action === \"delete\") {\n          if (!p.event_id) return json({ error: \"Missing event_id\" });\n          return json(await deleteEvent(client, p.event_id));\n        }\n        \n        return json({ error: `Unknown action: ${(p as any).action}` });\n      } catch (err) {\n        return json({ error: err instanceof Error ? err.message : String(err) });\n      }\n    },\n  }, { name: \"feishu_calendar\" });\n\n  api.logger.info?.(\"feishu_calendar: Registered\");\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772346894629}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f670845","parentId":"1a876b7f","timestamp":"2026-03-01T06:35:02.559Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了。代码中使用的是 `client.calendar.calendar.create`，但我记得飞书SDK中应该是 `client.calendar.event.create` 或者 `client.calendar.calendarEvent.create`。\n\n另外，`path: { calendar_id: \"primary\" }` 可能有问题，\"primary\" 可能不是有效的日历ID。应该使用具体的日历ID，或者用用户的默认日历。\n\n让我检查一下 SDK 的正确用法。应该是 `client.calendar.event.create` 或者 `client.calendar.calendarEvent.create`。\n\n还有一个问题是，创建事件时传入的 attendees 格式可能不对。飞书API要求的是 open_id，但是可能需要指定 `user_id_type: \"open_id\"`。\n\n让我修复这些问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！代码用的是 `client.calendar.calendar.create`，但SDK方法名可能是 `calendarEvent.create`。另外 `calendar_id: \"primary\"` 可能无效。让我修复："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit:99","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/src/calendar.ts","old_string":"const resp: any = await client.calendar.calendar.create({\n    path: { calendar_id: \"primary\" },\n    data: body,\n  });","new_string":"const resp: any = await client.calendar.event.create({\n    data: body,\n  });"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":1692,"output":261,"cacheRead":72704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772346894635}}
