{"type":"message","id":"9d572030","parentId":"468a8be2","timestamp":"2026-03-01T06:42:33.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"伟哥说日程是我曾经学会的第一个skill。让我去看看workspace里有没有feishu-calendar的skill文件。根据available_skills列表，有一个feishu-calendar skill在 ~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-calendar/SKILL.md","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_bdrk_01NUGQa1dMsH6JkRQFudRzee","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/openclaw/extensions/feishu/skills/feishu-calendar/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-5","usage":{"input":10,"output":163,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":117254,"totalTokens":117427,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772347331383}}
{"type":"message","id":"aba0ade2","parentId":"9d572030","timestamp":"2026-03-01T06:42:33.786Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_bdrk_01NUGQa1dMsH6JkRQFudRzee","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-calendar\ndescription: |\n  Feishu calendar event management. Create, update, delete, and retrieve calendar events. Requires calendar:calendar.event:create and related permissions.\n---\n\n# Feishu Calendar Tool\n\nManage Feishu calendar events using the `feishu_calendar` tool.\n\n## Actions\n\n### Create Event\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"create\",\n  \"summary\": \"教学中心集中办公\",\n  \"description\": \"教学中心集中办公讨论\",\n  \"start_time\": \"2025-03-02T10:00:00+08:00\",\n  \"end_time\": \"2025-03-02T16:00:00+08:00\",\n  \"location\": \"教学中心\",\n  \"attendees\": [\"ou_xxx\", \"ou_yyy\"]\n}\n```\n\n### Get Event\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"get\",\n  \"event_id\": \"event_xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n### Update Event\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"update\",\n  \"event_id\": \"event_xxx\",\n  \"summary\": \"Updated Title\",\n  \"start_time\": \"2025-03-02T11:00:00+08:00\"\n}\n```\n\n### Delete Event\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"delete\",\n  \"event_id\": \"event_xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n- `action` - Required: create, update, delete, get\n- `summary` - Event title\n- `description` - Event description\n- `start_time` - ISO 8601 timestamp (e.g., 2025-03-02T10:00:00+08:00)\n- `end_time` - ISO 8601 timestamp\n- `location` - Location name\n- `attendees` - Array of user open_ids\n- `visibility` - default, public, or private\n\n## Permissions Required\n\n- `calendar:calendar.event:create` - Create events\n- `calendar:calendar.event:update` - Update events\n- `calendar:calendar.event:delete` - Delete events\n- `calendar:calendar.event:read` - Read events\n\n## Usage Notes\n\n- Times should be in ISO 8601 format with timezone\n- Attendees should be user open_ids (not emails or names)\n- Use feishu_contact tool to find user open_ids\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772347353782}}
